<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>URL Shortener</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-start: #070a1e;
            --bg-end: #10162f;
            --panel: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.95);
            --panel-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            --text: #e8edf8;
            --muted: #9bb0d6;
            --accent: #2dd4ff;
            --accent-alt: #8b5cf6;
            --shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.08), transparent 20%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.14), transparent 18%),
                        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-start) 0%, var(--bg-end) 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: clamp(16px, 5vw, 32px);
            position: relative;
            overflow: auto;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.12), transparent 18%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.12), transparent 14%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 90%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04), transparent 24%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: min(680px, 95vw);
            padding: clamp(28px, 8vw, 52px);
            border-radius: clamp(20px, 5vw, 32px);
            background: rgba(8, 14, 32, 0.96);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .hero::before,
        .hero::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(90px);
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .hero::before {
            width: 260px;
            height: 260px;
            top: -80px;
            right: -90px;
            background: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.25);
        }

        .hero::after {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            bottom: -80px;
            left: -70px;
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.22);
        }

        .hero-head {
            margin-bottom: 38px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .hero-accent {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .hero-accent span {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .hero-icon {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 18px;
            border-radius: 26px;
            background: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.16);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.18);
            font-size: 32px;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-shadow: 0 0 26px rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.38);
        }

        .hero-title {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.8rem);
            line-height: 1.02;
            letter-spacing: -0.06em;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), #7c4dff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .hero-copy {
            margin: 16px auto 0;
            max-width: 520px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        .stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 28px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .stat-chip {
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
        }

        .form-panel {
            margin-top: clamp(32px, 6vw, 40px);
            background: rgba(11, 17, 39, 0.95);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border-radius: clamp(20px, 4vw, 26px);
            padding: clamp(24px, 6vw, 34px);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
        }

        .form-label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
        }

        .input-wrap {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
            gap: clamp(12px, 3vw, 16px);
            align-items: center;
        }

        .input-wrap input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: clamp(14px, 4vw, 18px) clamp(16px, 4vw, 22px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: clamp(16px, 4vw, 20px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            color: var(--text);
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1rem);
            transition: border-color 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease;
        }

        .input-wrap input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.6);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.14);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        .input-wrap input::placeholder {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.52);
        }

        .btn-submit {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: clamp(14px, 4vw, 18px) clamp(24px, 6vw, 32px);
            border: none;
            border-radius: clamp(16px, 4vw, 20px);
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2.5vw, 1rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #4f46e5);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, filter 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 18px 32px rgba(13, 60, 115, 0.32);
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            filter: brightness(1.08);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00c8ff, #5f5ee8);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 46px rgba(13, 60, 115, 0.36);
        }

        .btn-submit:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .btn-submit::after {
            content: '→';
            margin-left: 10px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover::after {
            transform: translateX(3px);
        }

        .generated-url {
            margin: 0 0 28px 0;
            padding: 18px 22px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.12), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08));
            border: 1px solid rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.35);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.15), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            color: var(--accent);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.6;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: slideIn 0.4s ease-out;
        }

        .generated-url::before {
            content: '✓';
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .generated-url a {
            color: var(--accent);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            word-break: break-all;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: background 0.2s ease;
        }

        .generated-url a:hover {
            background: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.15);
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-12px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Large Desktop */
        @media (min-width: 1200px) {
            .hero {
                max-width: 720px;
                padding: 60px;
            }

            .hero-title {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }

            .form-panel {
                padding: 40px;
            }
        }

        /* Desktop */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero {
                max-width: 650px;
                padding: 48px 36px;
            }

            .hero::before {
                width: 240px;
                height: 240px;
                top: -70px;
                right: -80px;
            }

            .hero::after {
                width: 180px;
                height: 180px;
                bottom: -70px;
                left: -60px;
            }

            .hero-icon {
                width: 76px;
                height: 76px;
                font-size: 30px;
            }

            .hero-title {
                font-size: 3.4rem;
            }

            .form-panel {
                padding: 32px;
            }
        }

        /* Tablet */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                max-width: 90vw;
                padding: 40px 32px;
            }

            .hero::before {
                width: 200px;
                height: 200px;
                top: -60px;
                right: -70px;
            }

            .hero::after {
                width: 160px;
                height: 160px;
                bottom: -60px;
                left: -50px;
            }

            .hero-icon {
                width: 70px;
                height: 70px;
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }

            .hero-title {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .hero-copy {
                font-size: 1.05rem;
            }

            .form-panel {
                padding: 28px;
            }

            .stats {
                gap: 8px;
            }

            .stat-chip {
                padding: 8px 14px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }

        /* Large Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 680px) {
            .hero {
                padding: 34px 24px;
            }

            .hero::before {
                width: 180px;
                height: 180px;
                top: -50px;
                right: -60px;
            }

            .hero::after {
                width: 140px;
                height: 140px;
                bottom: -50px;
                left: -40px;
            }

            .hero-icon {
                width: 68px;
                height: 68px;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.6rem;
            }

            .hero-copy {
                font-size: 1rem;
                line-height: 1.7;
            }

            .form-panel {
                padding: 26px 22px;
                margin-top: 32px;
            }

            .input-wrap {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 14px;
            }

            .btn-submit {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 16px;
            }

            .stats {
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 8px;
                margin-top: 24px;
            }

            .stat-chip {
                padding: 8px 12px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }

            .generated-url {
                padding: 16px 18px;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                margin-bottom: 24px;
            }
        }

        /* Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            body {
                padding: 16px;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 28px 20px;
                border-radius: 20px;
                max-width: 95vw;
            }

            .hero::before {
                width: 140px;
                height: 140px;
                top: -40px;
                right: -50px;
            }

            .hero::after {
                width: 120px;
                height: 120px;
                bottom: -40px;
                left: -30px;
            }

            .hero-icon {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .hero-accent {
                padding: 8px 14px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
                margin-bottom: 16px;
            }

            .hero-copy {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                line-height: 1.8;
                margin: 12px auto 0;
            }

            .form-panel {
                padding: 22px 18px;
                margin-top: 28px;
                border-radius: 18px;
            }

            .form-label {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                margin-bottom: 12px;
            }

            .input-wrap {
                gap: 12px;
            }

            .input-wrap input {
                padding: 14px 16px;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }

            .btn-submit {
                padding: 14px;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }

            .stats {
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                margin-top: 20px;
                gap: 6px;
            }

            .stat-chip {
                padding: 6px 10px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }

            .generated-url {
                padding: 14px 16px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
        }

        /* Small Mobile */
        @media (max-width: 375px) {
            body {
                padding: 12px;
            }

            .hero {
                padding: 24px 16px;
                border-radius: 16px;
            }

            .hero::before,
            .hero::after {
                display: none;
            }

            .hero-icon {
                width: 56px;
                height: 56px;
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .hero-accent {
                padding: 6px 12px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
                margin-bottom: 14px;
            }

            .hero-copy {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                line-height: 1.7;
                margin: 10px auto 0;
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .form-panel {
                padding: 18px 16px;
                margin-top: 24px;
                border-radius: 16px;
            }

            .form-label {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .input-wrap {
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .input-wrap input {
                padding: 12px 14px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                border-radius: 14px;
            }

            .btn-submit {
                padding: 12px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                border-radius: 14px;
            }

            .stats {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                margin-top: 18px;
                gap: 4px;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }

            .stat-chip {
                padding: 5px 8px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
            }

            .generated-url {
                padding: 12px 14px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                margin-bottom: 18px;
                border-radius: 14px;
            }
        }

        /* Enhanced Table Styles */
        .url-table {
            margin-top: clamp(32px, 6vw, 40px);
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: clamp(16px, 3vw, 20px);
            background: rgba(11, 17, 39, 0.95);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
            overflow: hidden;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }

        .url-table table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 0.95rem);
        }

        .url-table thead {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.1), rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08));
        }

        .url-table th {
            padding: clamp(16px, 3vw, 20px) clamp(12px, 2vw, 16px);
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--accent);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.5vw, 0.9rem);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .url-table td {
            padding: clamp(14px, 3vw, 18px) clamp(12px, 2vw, 16px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
            color: var(--text);
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .url-table tbody tr {
            transition: background 0.2s ease;
        }

        .url-table tbody tr:hover {
            background: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.04);
        }

        .url-table tbody tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .url-table .short-id {
            font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
            background: rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(45, 212, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: clamp(6px, 1.5vw, 8px);
            padding: clamp(4px, 1vw, 6px) clamp(8px, 2vw, 12px);
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: clamp(0.75rem, 1.5vw, 0.85rem);
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 2px 0;
            word-break: break-all;
        }

        .url-table .redirect-url {
            color: var(--muted);
            word-break: break-all;
            max-width: clamp(200px, 40vw, 300px);
            font-size: clamp(0.8rem, 1.5vw, 0.9rem);
        }

        .url-table .clicks {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--accent);
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
            border-radius: clamp(8px, 2vw, 12px);
            padding: clamp(3px, 0.8vw, 4px) clamp(8px, 2vw, 10px);
            display: inline-block;
            min-width: clamp(32px, 6vw, 40px);
        }

        .url-table .sno {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--muted);
            text-align: center;
            width: clamp(40px, 8vw, 60px);
        }

        .table-header {
            margin-bottom: clamp(16px, 3vw, 20px);
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--muted);
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.1rem);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .table-header::before {
            content: '📊';
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        /* Table Responsive Breakpoints */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .url-table .redirect-url {
                max-width: 250px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .url-table {
                margin-top: 32px;
                border-radius: 16px;
                overflow-x: auto;
            }

            .url-table table {
                min-width: 600px;
            }

            .url-table th,
            .url-table td {
                padding: 14px 10px;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .url-table .redirect-url {
                max-width: 200px;
            }

            .url-table .short-id {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                padding: 4px 8px;
            }

            .url-table .clicks {
                padding: 3px 8px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }

            .table-header {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 680px) {
            .url-table {
                margin-top: 28px;
            }

            .url-table th,
            .url-table td {
                padding: 12px 8px;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
            }

            .url-table .redirect-url {
                max-width: 180px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }

            .url-table .short-id {
                font-size: 0.75rem;
                padding: 3px 6px;
            }

            .url-table .clicks {
                padding: 2px 6px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                min-width: 32px;
            }

            .url-table .sno {
                width: 40px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            .url-table {
                margin-top: 24px;
                border-radius: 12px;
            }

            .url-table th,
            .url-table td {
                padding: 10px 6px;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
            }

            .url-table .redirect-url {
                max-width: 140px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
            }

            .url-table .short-id {
                font-size: 0.7rem;
                padding: 2px 4px;
            }

            .url-table .clicks {
                padding: 2px 4px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
                min-width: 28px;
            }

            .url-table .sno {
                width: 35px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
            }

            .table-header {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                margin-bottom: 14px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 375px) {
            .url-table {
                margin-top: 20px;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .url-table th,
            .url-table td {
                padding: 8px 4px;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
            }

            .url-table .redirect-url {
                max-width: 120px;
                font-size: 0.7rem;
            }

            .url-table .short-id {
                font-size: 0.65rem;
                padding: 2px 3px;
            }

            .url-table .clicks {
                padding: 1px 3px;
                font-size: 0.7rem;
                min-width: 24px;
            }

            .url-table .sno {
                width: 30px;
                font-size: 0.7rem;
            }

            .table-header {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                margin-bottom: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="hero">
        <% if(locals.id) { %>
        <p class="generated-url">Your short URL: <a href="https://url-shortner-harsh.onrender.com/url/<%= id %>" target="_blank">https://url-shortner-harsh.onrender.com/url/<%= id %></a></p>
        <% } %>
            <div class="hero-icon" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 2rem;">🔗</div>
        <header class="hero-head">
            <div class="hero-accent"><span>Live Link Builder</span></div>
            <h1 class="hero-title">URL Shortener</h1>
            <p class="hero-copy">Transform long, messy links into short, memorable URLs that are easy to share and fast to load.</p>
            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat-chip">Fast generation</div>
                <div class="stat-chip">Secure redirects</div>
                <div class="stat-chip">Minimal interface</div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="form-panel">
            <form method="POST" action="/url">
                <label class="form-label" for="url">Original website URL</label>
                <div class="input-wrap">
                    <input type="text" name="url" placeholder="https://example.com" required>
                    <button class="btn-submit" type="submit">Generate Short URL</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
        <% if(locals.urls && urls.length > 0){ %>
            <div class="url-table">
                <div class="table-header" style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 10px;">Your Shortened URLs</div>
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="sno">#</th>
                            <th>Short ID</th>
                            <th>Original URL</th>
                            <th>Clicks</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <% urls.forEach((url, index) => { %>
                            <tr>
                                <td class="sno"><%= index+1 %></td>
                                <td><span class="short-id"><%= url.shortId %></span></td>
                                <td><span class="redirect-url"><%= url.redirectURL %></span></td>
                                <td><span class="clicks"><%= url.visitHistory.length %></span></td>
                            </tr>
                        <% }) %>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        <%} %>
    </section>
</body>
</html>